==制作==
=== 选角 ===
《白宫陷落》剧组成员巴特勒、艾克哈特、弗里曼、贝瑟、里奥和米切尔宣布回归出演本剧<ref name="London, Butler and others">{{Cite web |url=http://collider.com/olympus-has-fallen-sequel-london-has-fallen-gerard-butler/ |title=Gerard Butler, Morgan Freeman, and Aaron Eckhart Returning for OLYMPUS HAS FALLEN Sequel LONDON HAS FALLEN |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106121132/http://collider.com/olympus-has-fallen-sequel-london-has-fallen-gerard-butler/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。制作定于2015年5月在伦敦启动，克莱顿·罗森博格和凯特琳·班尼迪克特回归编剧。导演[[安东尼·福奎阿|安东尼·福奎阿]]因执导《[[伸冤人|伸冤人]]》而没能回归<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.screendaily.com/festivals/afm/afm-news/london-has-fallen-heads-to-afm/5063031.article |title=London Has Fallen Heads to AFM |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041406/http://www.screendaily.com/festivals/afm/afm-news/london-has-fallen-heads-to-afm/5063031.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年5月1日，据报道叫电影院收购了续集的发行权，将于2015年10月2日上映本片<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/focus-features-dates-olympus-sequel-london-has-fallen-for-october-2015/ |title=Focus Features Dates 'Olympus' Sequel 'London Has Fallen' For October 2015 |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2013-03-22 |accessdate=2014-05-01 |archive-date=2014-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503065558/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/focus-features-dates-olympus-sequel-london-has-fallen-for-october-2015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年8月18日，据宣布《[[查理必死|查理必死]]》的导演弗雷德里克·邦德将接替福奎阿的位置<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/fredrik-bond-olympus-has-fallen-sequel-1201285643/|title=Fredrik Bond to Direct ‘Olympus Has Fallen’ Sequel|publisher=Variety|date=2014-08-18|accessdate=2014-08-19|archive-date=2014-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820202240/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/fredrik-bond-olympus-has-fallen-sequel-1201285643/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但邦德在开机前六周前的9月18日离开剧组<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title='Olympus Has Fallen' Sequel Loses Its Director|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/olympus-has-fallen-sequel-loses-734224|accessdate=2014-09-19|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-09-18|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530123728/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/olympus-has-fallen-sequel-loses-734224|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月28日，导演巴巴克·纳加菲签约直到本片<ref name=NajafiLeo>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Troubled 'Olympus Has Fallen' Sequel Finds Director|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/troubled-olympus-has-fallen-sequel-736224|accessdate=2014-09-29|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-09-28|archive-date=2014-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141002015918/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/troubled-olympus-has-fallen-sequel-736224|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月10日，杰基·厄尔·哈利签约饰演警察局长曼森<ref name=Haley>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|title=‘Olympus Has Fallen’ Sequel Lands Jackie Earle Haley As First New Cast Member|url=http://www.thewrap.com/olympus-has-fallen-sequel-lands-jackie-earle-haley-as-first-new-cast-member-exclusive/|accessdate=2014-10-11|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2014-10-10|archive-date=2014-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010220238/http://www.thewrap.com/olympus-has-fallen-sequel-lands-jackie-earle-haley-as-first-new-cast-member-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月12日，麦赫迪·德比饰演苏丹·曼苏尔，在无人机空袭后彻底改变人生的三兄弟中最年轻的一个<ref name=DehbiCast>{{cite news|last1=Yamato|first1=Jen|title=‘London Has Fallen’ Adds ‘Tyrant’ Thesp|url=http://deadline.com/2014/11/wonder-woman-suicide-squad-london-has-fallen-paper-towns-casting-1201282960/|accessdate=2014-11-13|publisher=deadline.com|date=2014-11-12|archive-date=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127230201/http://deadline.com/2014/11/wonder-woman-suicide-squad-london-has-fallen-paper-towns-casting-1201282960/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
2014年10月24日，主体摄影在伦敦启动<ref name="filmingandcast">{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/london-has-fallen-begins-filming/5079401.article?referrer=RSS|title=London Has Fallen begins filming|publisher=Screen Daily|first=Michael|last=Rosser|date=2014-11-03|accessdate=2014-11-03|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192230/http://www.screendaily.com/news/london-has-fallen-begins-filming/5079401.article?referrer=RSS|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NickMcArdle>{{cite web|url=https://instagram.com/p/uiF4n4kqUP/|title=First day of filming "London Has Fallen" sequel to "Olympus Has Fallen". Gerard Butler and Morgan Freeman|date=2014-10-24|website=Nick McArdle on Instagram|accessdate=2016-06-11|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210254/https://www.instagram.com/p/uiF4n4kqUP/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。圣诞节休息前展开了为期四周的摄制，弗里曼、艾克哈特和里奥有份参与。10月份拍摄《[[人造天劫|人造天劫]]》的杰拉德·巴特勒后来加入剧组，于2015年3月一同与艾克哈特拍戏<ref name="Filming">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2981342/Gerard-Butler-hits-London-Fallen-set-Aaron-Eckhart.html|title=A bloodied Gerard Butler hits the London Has Fallen set wearing a battered suit and tie with co-star Aaron Eckhart|publisher=Daily Mail.com|first=Hanna|last=Flint|date=2015-03-05|accessdate=2015-03-07|archive-date=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310053727/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2981342/Gerard-Butler-hits-London-Fallen-set-Aaron-Eckhart.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。通常用来举办伦敦时装周和夏季电影放映活动的直升飞机停靠在[[萨默塞特府|萨默塞特府]]的院子里<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2986086/Helicopter-makes-dramatic-landing-London-s-Somerset-House-Gerard-Butler-continues-filming-new-movie.html|title=PICTURED: Helicopter makes a dramatic landing at Somerset House as Gerard Butler continues filming his new movie London Has Fallen|publisher=Daily Mail.com|date=2015-03-09|accessdate=2015-03-10|archive-date=2015-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310011306/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2986086/Helicopter-makes-dramatic-landing-London-s-Somerset-House-Gerard-Butler-continues-filming-new-movie.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，巴特勒和安琪拉·贝瑟在萨默塞特府被人看见<ref name=Roar>{{cite web|url=http://roarnews.co.uk/wordpress/?p=17044|title=PICS: Gerard Butler spotted speeding down Strand in filming of action thriller|website=Roar News|date=2015-03-08|accessdate=2015-03-08|archive-date=2015-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312045201/http://roarnews.co.uk/wordpress/?p=17044|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴特拉在采访中表示电影还会在印度和保加利亚拍摄<ref name=SaudiBeauty>{{cite web|last1=Haq|first1=Nilo|title=Interview with Gerard Butler in Dubai|url=http://saudibeautyblog.com/interview-with-gerard-butler-in-dubai/|website=Saudi Beauty blog|location=Dubai|date=2015-03-31|quote=Eye candy Gerard Butler is the new ambassador for Boss Bottled|access-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201164501/http://saudibeautyblog.com/interview-with-gerard-butler-in-dubai/|archive-date=2016-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。剧组在保加利亚博雅那电影中心拍摄时，[[保加利亚|保加利亞]]總統[[罗森·普列夫内利耶夫|罗森·普列夫内利耶夫]]前往探班<ref>{{cite web|url=http://btvnovinite.bg/article/bulgaria/plevneliev-tri-pati-poveche-filmi-mozhe-da-se-snimat-u-nas.html|website=btv Новините|date=24 March 2015|accessdate=19 April 2015|title=Плевнелиев: Три пъти повече филми може да се снимат у нас|language=bg|archive-date=2015-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427124806/http://btvnovinite.bg/article/bulgaria/plevneliev-tri-pati-poveche-filmi-mozhe-da-se-snimat-u-nas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=BulgarianPrez>{{cite web|title=Bulgarian President visits London Has Fallen|url=http://gerardbutlergals.com/content/press/bulgarian-president-visits-london-has-fallen/|website=Gerard Butler GALS|location=Bulgaria|date=2015-03-24|accessdate=2015-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427124912/http://gerardbutlergals.com/content/press/bulgarian-president-visits-london-has-fallen/|archive-date=2015-04-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。12月份杀青<ref name="NajafiLeo" />。

