==發行==
原定2015年10月2日發布，但後來[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]與Gramercy Pictures改至2016年1月22日，為了避免與《[[絕地救援|絕地救援]]》競爭<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lesnick|first1=Silas|title=London Has Fallen Has Moved to 2016|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/449899-london-has-fallen-has-moved-to-2016#/slide/1|accessdate=June 12, 2015|publisher=ComingSoon.net|date=June 12, 2015|archive-date=2015-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150615030254/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/449899-london-has-fallen-has-moved-to-2016#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Fox Switches ‘The Martian’ and ‘Victor Frankenstein’ Release Dates |url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/fox-switches-the-martian-and-victor-frankenstein-release-dates-1201441061/ |accessdate=June 12, 2015 |date=June 10, 2015 |archive-date=2015-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614074009/https://deadline.com/2015/06/fox-switches-the-martian-and-victor-frankenstein-release-dates-1201441061/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2015年9月16日，為了需要更多時間來完成特效，因此又延至2016年3月4日<ref>{{cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=‘London Has Fallen’ On A New Release Date: Gerard Butler Action Film To Open March 4, 2016|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/london-has-fallen-release-date-change-march-2016-1201530670/|accessdate=September 18, 2015|work=deadline.com|date=September 16, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118003826/http://deadline.com/2015/09/london-has-fallen-release-date-change-march-2016-1201530670/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度26%，基於191條評論，平均分為3.96/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/london_has_fallen/ |title=London Has Fallen (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=March 3, 2016 |archive-date=2017-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130152301/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/london_has_fallen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上僅得到28分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/london-has-fallen |title=London Has Fallen reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=March 3, 2016 |archive-date=2017-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802174712/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/london-has-fallen |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得5.9分，普遍不受專業影評人認同。

===票房===
在美國和加拿大，據預測，電影於首週末將會從3250間戲院中獲得約2000至2300萬美元的票房，可能輸於同時推出的新片《[[動物方城市|動物方城市]]》（約6000至7000萬美元），但可擊敗《探戈，戰地，威士忌》（約1000萬至1200萬美元）<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-london-has-fallen-box-office-preview-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-deadpool-1201712794/ |title=Disney Unleashed: ‘Zootopia’ Toon Expected To Roar Past $60M – Weekend Preview |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303095024/https://deadline.com/2016/03/zootopia-london-has-fallen-box-office-preview-whiskey-tango-foxtrot-deadpool-1201712794/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首週票房收入為2200萬美元，位居冠軍《[[動物方城市|動物方城市]]》（7500萬美元）之後。臺北首週票房為1263萬新臺幣，位居當週冠軍。

在中国大陆，首周四天获得1.59亿人民币列第二位，最终票房3.39億人民币<ref>[http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/248896 《伦敦陷落》電影介紹] {{Wayback|url=http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/248896 |date=20180215144005 }} 貓眼票房</ref>。

